targets.expr: sum by (type) (ataccama_one_mmm_jobs_duration_partial_seconds_sum{type=~"DQ.*", status="RUNNING", exitStatus="FINISHED", namespace=~"$namespace"}) / sum by (type, namespace) (ataccama_one_mmm_jobs_duration_partial_seconds_count{type=~"DQ.*", status="RUNNING", exitStatus="FINISHED", namespace=~"$namespace"})

sum by (operation) (ataccama_one_mmm_mdoperations_time_seconds_sum{operation=~".*monitoringproject\\.storage\\.operation\\.results(.*)", namespace=~"$namespace"}) / sum by (operation) (ataccama_one_mmm_mdoperations_time_seconds_count{operation=~".*monitoringproject\\.storage\\.operation\\.results(.*)", namespace=~"$namespace"})
